Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.02,0:27:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.35,0:27:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.74,0:27:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.01,0:27:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告訴我這房子怎么了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.18,0:27:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先告訴我  你的怪物是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.88,0:27:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.98,0:28:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.94,0:28:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.53,0:28:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  令人不安
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.00,0:28:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的寵物魚居然在跟你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.39,0:28:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但時間是金錢  艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.36,0:28:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.35,0:28:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水需要換了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.71,0:28:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活在魚缸里  根本就沒什么"變"可言
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.51,0:28:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這輩子一直待在這里面
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的整個世界就在你小桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.93,0:29:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我環顧四周  每一天都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.08,0:29:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈光  家具
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.97,0:29:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至聲音  總是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.82,0:29:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我處于循環之中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.10,0:29:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非我死去  循環無法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.38,0:29:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受夠了這世界
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.01,0:29:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做什么  我想幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.00,0:29:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這很明顯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.97,0:29:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也就只能為一只魚缸里的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.97,0:29:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑魚做一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.65,0:29:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.06,0:29:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他搬到窗邊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.67,0:29:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安吉拉  他是我的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.03,0:29:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.87,0:29:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.18,0:29:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.22,0:30:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃下去
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.99,0:30:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.88,0:30:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常燙  吃的時候請小心
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.66,0:30:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸著名的樹莓派  慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.48,0:30:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.41,0:30:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.74,0:30:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意  艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.52,0:30:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾略特  我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.62,0:30:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.57,0:31:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.39,0:31:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是說了他們想聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.49,0:32:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會那么做的  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.78,0:32:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變世界
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.13,0:32:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜到了  你才一個月大
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.97,0:32:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.45,0:32:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕你的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.43,0:32:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那是什么嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.26,0:32:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不配套
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.67,0:32:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.60,0:32:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還不明顯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.38,0:32:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.62,0:32:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.68,0:32:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.18,0:32:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.13,0:33:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.02,0:33:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我唯一的朋友的臉孔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.81,0:33:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.51,0:33:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這兒  你是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.88,0:33:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.21,0:33:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.43,0:33:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.03,0:33:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.46,0:34:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.64,0:34:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.82,0:34:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪都不會去的  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.07,0:34:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會一起走到底
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.70,0:34:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是好好走路吧  你似乎不太會跳芭蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.84,0:34:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  去你的  小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.21,0:34:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老子的曲膝不比任何人差
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.43,0:34:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒忙著敲鍵盤的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.94,0:34:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在教同學這樣的舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.90,0:34:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.24,0:34:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝搭救
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.67,0:35:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾他沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.82,0:35:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.71,0:35:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是社會禍害
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.62,0:35:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.39,0:35:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-等等  你去哪  -是他
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.89,0:36:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機  馬上拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.59,0:36:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給他
