Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.66,0:36:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz331.1\move(132.6,109.6,124.8,99.2,0,314)}{\fn方正准圆_GBK\fs16\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H787E6D&}奧利
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.36,0:36:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么還在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.83,0:36:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再過4小時  我就得去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.31,0:36:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會十分懷念這份工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.44,0:36:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今后要怎么掙錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.50,0:36:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是...去做個性感服務員唄
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.09,0:36:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.28,0:36:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興你喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.34,0:36:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我很高興打工掙錢之前
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.30,0:36:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能再這么玩一次
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.33,0:36:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.07,0:36:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.37,0:37:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不清
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.29,0:37:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始新工作之前我總會很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.95,0:37:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我絕對不擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.55,0:37:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.69,0:37:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份工作不合適  我就另找一份
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.86,0:37:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.04,0:37:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你經常擔心  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.96,0:37:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.24,0:37:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.84,0:37:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那個狠角色了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.45,0:38:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是你這輩子唯一該擔心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.10,0:38:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我找你找得多辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.52,0:38:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.95,0:38:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.99,0:38:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.35,0:38:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才像話
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.49,0:38:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我黑暗空虛的生活中的一縷陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.49,0:38:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真詩意
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.95,0:38:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這不叫道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.30,0:38:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.09,0:39:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我甩了你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.94,0:39:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴你  你要惹火我了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.51,0:39:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我想跟你共度一生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.93,0:39:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真混蛋死了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.39,0:39:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大事要發生了  西斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.23,0:39:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明天就得行動
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.38,0:39:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是唯一的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.10,0:39:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就沒機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.42,0:39:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說真的  達琳
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.69,0:39:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.36,0:39:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你以為你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.51,0:39:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放世界  解救眾生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.60,0:39:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雇我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.48,0:39:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的動機可不是那么高尚
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.16,0:39:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.70,0:39:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.43,0:39:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.51,0:39:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這對我多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.50,0:40:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.83,0:40:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他們談談
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.04,0:40:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我姑媽艾斯特的惡習都用這個治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.75,0:40:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,液體抗腹瀉劑  治你的...那個
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.51,0:40:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬和鹽補充電解質
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.99,0:40:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解充血藥止鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.88,0:40:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都第三杯了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.87,0:40:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來七杯  你就精神煥發了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.58,0:40:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把車開過來
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.90,0:40:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他繼續喝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.03,0:40:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.59,0:40:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.85,0:40:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又見了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.66,0:40:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幾沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.57,0:40:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做我們做的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.21,0:40:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你了  你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.27,0:40:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你走開了  還是我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.97,0:41:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許我們都走開了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.68,0:41:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也或者都沒  無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.38,0:41:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些充滿希望的時刻嚇到我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.98,0:41:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了  后臺程序  記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.17,0:41:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚  會有一項"無需用戶操作程序"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.15,0:41:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現  讓我措手不及
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.78,0:41:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虛高真低的轉盤會繼續轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.50,0:41:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我確定
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.46,0:43:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后臺程序  他們不會停止運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.38,0:44:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們總是活躍的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.07,0:44:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們誘惑  操控
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.78,0:44:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們主宰我們
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.95,0:44:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡管你在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.00,0:44:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡管我創造了你  也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.17,0:44:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都得獨自面對他們
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.23,0:44:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們最多只能期望
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.18,0:44:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切之中唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.54,0:44:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我們撐過去時
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.66,0:44:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會看到有幾個熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.41,0:44:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊等我們
